videos.headline: Kentucky WR Bouvier fools DB on route to 1st TD of game
videos.description: Kentucky QB Terry Wilson connects with David Bouvier off his back leg to take an early lead against Florida.

videos.headline: Florida stops Kentucky momentum with fumble recovery
videos.description: Florida recovers a fumble from Kentucky running back Terry Wilson with five minutes remaining in the half.

videos.headline: Wilson fools entire defense on fake flip, runs it in for TD
videos.description: Kentucky QB Terry Wilson fools the defense on a fake flip, then runs 24 yards for the score.

videos.headline: Florida sideline is irate after controversial missed FG
videos.description: Refs call a Florida field goal attempt no good, despite replays showing it may have curled inside the post.

videos.headline: Kentucky ends game on wild TD, gets 1st win vs. Gators since 86'
videos.description: Kentucky's win ends unusually with a forced fumble returned for a TD and a Wildcats' victory against the Gators for the first time since 1986.
